---
title: Sichuan Chicken Bowl with Garlic Rice & Soy Mayo
description: Why did anyone cross the road? To get a taste of this sensational chicken dish, of course! With our signature mild Sichuan
garlic paste, soy mayo and fragrant garlic rice, it's a perfect mix of flavours that’ll spice up your midweek routine.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/sichuan-chicken-rice-bowl-aaeae6b8.jpg
